                    <span class="inline-block mb-3 text-primary uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-medium">About This Journey</span>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-medium mb-5 leading-tight decorative-line">
                        About This Experience
                    </h2>
                    <div class="content-card p-8 bg-white">
